{"tid":2251903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳帆哽咽回應國泰裁員：政府已要求國泰照顧員工福祉","createTime":"2020-10-21T06:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:09:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":224,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4573967d28ccb41f03f9e927638f98d17efb08","tid":2251903,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"國泰航空宣佈重組，裁減5000多名駐港員工，運輸及房屋局長陳帆對數以千計員工失去工作感到難過，又指對香港固有品牌國泰港龍停運感到可惜，言談間一度哽咽，強調政府已要求國泰照顧員工福祉，維持核心團隊及人才，為未來整裝再上做好準備。   <br />\n<br />\n陳帆指，政府投資國泰目的是維護香港長遠作爲國際航空樞紐地位的競爭力，並非只為單一航空公司的前景，財政司委派2名觀察員入董事局，只負責理解集團營運，並不會參與日常營運和商業決定。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362551&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=a1e4bd6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362551</a>"},{"pid":"39101904ce08848b47ead103c0c513e41aaf02a4","tid":2251903,"uid":207057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8af02a2834d9b706907fba1ac8872cdac87c3d","tid":2251903,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f37d703ffea66489f0d24deadcb4866df8a9213","tid":2251903,"uid":77196,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ed22199bb551951d93055943fcc450675f3825","tid":2251903,"uid":260251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif